Enrolments by school,"Enrolments in SA Government schools collected as part of the annual enrolment data collection in Term 3. Enrolments are full-time equivalents (FTE) from 2009.

Important notes:

*	To protect the confidentiality of students, where a school has 5 or less students, student enrolments are suppressed for that school.

*	Nil enrolment FTE may indicate a school closure or amalgamation.

*	Longitude and latitude for closed schools have not been provided.
