Social Housing – new households housed,"Datasets present number of new households housed in Public Housing (PH) and State Owned and Managed Indigenous Housing (SOMIH) across Local Government Areas (LGAs) in South Australia in a financial year.

PH and SOMIH refers to dwellings owned and managed by the SA Housing Authority. These rentals are accessed by those on low income and/or with special needs. 

